        {
            "_id": "auVLK7MxrfP8W4Xl",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Mounted Volley",
            "sort": 700000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The outriders draw or reload their longbows, then launch a volley of arrows at creatures in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 100 feet, dealing @Damage[3d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:22|basic] save). When the squadron is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "sALnPt2WV8XV6F8v",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Shatter Shadows",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The outriders are within an area of magical darkness</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The outriders call on the power wielded by Iriatykis, attempting to dispel any darkness effects in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20] with a [[/r 1d20+14 #Counteract]]{+14} counteract modifier and a counteract rank of 4th. Each successfully counteracted effect explodes in a storm of tenebrous fragments, inflicting @Damage[2d6[spirit]|options:area-damage] damage to enemies in a @Template[type:burst|distance:20] centered on the effect (@Check[reflex|dc:22] save). Velstracs and worshippers of Zon-Kuthon get an outcome one degree worse than the result of their rolls on this saving throw.</p>"
                },
                "frequency": {
                    "max": 1,
                    "per": "day"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "concentrate",
                        "manipulate",
                        "occult"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "0DqJnTG0QE7xDUqg",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneThreeActions.webp",
            "name": "Skewering Strikes",
            "sort": 900000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The outriders plunge their longspears at enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] (@Check[reflex|dc:22|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[1d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d8+6)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(2d8+11)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
                },
