            "privateNotes": "",
            "publicNotes": "<p>Named for Horselord Iriatykis, forger of the mythic spear <em>Shadowpiercer</em> and instigator of the most successful rebellion against Nidal's shadowy overlords in living memory, these grimly determined riders seek to resist the brutal authority of the Umbral Court over the lands and peoples they call their own. While their efforts have mostly been focused on liberating rural communities on the nation's outskirts thus far, they have also begun targeted strikes against mercenary bands and supply caravans traveling through Nidal on their way to aid the Chelaxian war effort.</p>",
